{"tid":1675040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日醫護集會唔止醫護人員，全部人都應該去","createTime":"2019-10-25T15:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T10:09:40.000Z","uid":58998,"like":124,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"0c71b8a45e02379312023b536f6af469504fbc0d","tid":1675040,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:11:36.000Z","msg":"班醫護人員係今次運動真係付出好多<br />\n除咗記者，佢地真係算行得最前線嘅職業<br />\n諗下由六月起班陳沛然醫生同一班爆料醫護點樣揭穿醫院有後門俾警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下六月起警犬係醫院大搜捕，班黃絲醫護點幫手幫班義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下杏林覺醒等組織知道義士唔敢去醫院，點提供義診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下前線有幾多急救係醫生護士，冒著俾人拉嘅風險出嚟幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下前線俾人拉咗嘅醫生，人地搵大把錢照行咁前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下佢地敢頂著班藍絲上司係醫院戴黑口罩，叫你係老細面前認自己係黃都未必敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下班知名醫生同公會點樣屌狗濫暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下散仔王點屌班醫護怠慢啲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求奇都數到咁多，聽日仲要有不反，你唔係唔撐呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港醫護基本上係惟一仲未被赤化嘅專業，依家唔撐，第日中共一定會大換血變哂大陸醫生護士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Tq37GJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Tq37GJ.jpg&h=a811ebbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a91acf1be2a0591ef0d08a44bfd4379605d7b56","tid":1675040,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99aca581f827491aabc86bb9d414618ef78ed2c","tid":1675040,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislik